strings.Value: "That frog thing in the lake... watcha call it... it's weird — something green and slimy messing with so many people's heads!"
"The fey have their own ways of dealing with mortals. Take care not to get caught by such a frog yourself!"
"Nixies are famous tricksters. And I've heard they drown any victims who resist their tricks."
"The nixie's ridiculous appearance has always filled me with disgust and curiosity at the same time. I wonder what kind of zombies they'd make..."
"I've never met a fey before – but now I see they're more dangerous than genies. That tiny water girl subdued those wood-cutters so easily!"
